          <l>You took a step back</l>
          <l>Without me, without me, without me</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>And he's long gone</l>
          <l>When he's next to me</l>
          <l>And I realize the blame is on me</l>
        </lg>
