          <l>So shame on me now</l>
          <l>Flew me to places i'd never been</l>
          <l>Now i'm lying on the cold hard ground</l>
          <l>Oh, oh, trouble, trouble, trouble</l>
          <l>Oh, oh, trouble, trouble, trouble</l>
        </lg>
